=========
EpubMaker
=========

EpubMaker is the tool used for format conversion at Project Gutenberg.
It builds EPUB2 and Kindle files from HTML.
Also it builds HTML4, EPUB2, Kindle, and PDF files from reST sources.


Prerequisites
=============

* Python >= 2.6,

* HTMLTidy, 

* Kindlegen, 

* TexLive, and

* groff.
